## CORS Configuration

```typescript
import cors from 'cors';

app.use(cors({
  origin: process.env.NODE_ENV === 'production'
    ? ['https://yourapp.com']
    : ['http://localhost:3000'],
  credentials: true,
  methods: ['GET', 'POST', 'PUT', 'DELETE', 'PATCH'],
  allowedHeaders: ['Content-Type', 'Authorization'],
}));
```

