## Checklist

- [ ] Request/response types are validated with Zod or io-ts
- [ ] Error handling uses custom error classes
- [ ] Global error handler returns consistent format
- [ ] Async handlers wrap async route handlers
- [ ] Authentication middleware is type-safe
- [ ] API documentation with Swagger/OpenAPI
- [ ] Rate limiting protects against abuse
- [ ] CORS is configured for production
